Files in lib/quickstream/blocks/

All files in lib/quickstream/blocks/ are related to quickstream block
plugins.  quickstream block plugins usually manifest themselves is DSO
(dynamic shared object) files and sometimes other related metadata
files.


  Directories:


   - tests/ contains blocks that are not necessarily useful to users.
            They are blocks that are used in test programs that run
            from ../../../tests/.  Something like unit development tests.

   - filters/: filters are plugin blocks that have stream input and/or
               stream output.

   - controllers/: controllers are plugin blocks that do not have stream
                   input or stream output.

